snippet.title: Warp Academy
snippet.description:
Warp Academy is a global, online community of music producers, founded by Ableton Certified Trainers and industry experts.  We teach all flavors of electronic music production and performance with cutting-edge online courses and live-streams.  You can learn what you want, when you want, at your own pace.

Soundbanks are also a big part of our arsenal.  Expert sound designers on our team have built the essential tools you need to write music.  

You can learn almost any topic by searching our database of hundreds of free tutorial videos and production tools.  Come check us out.  We’re stoked to meet you!
